### ===========================
### Auth API Tests
### ===========================
 
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/auth
 
 
### -----------------------------------------------
### 1. Register
### -----------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/register
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
    "name": "Kyu Won",
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "Password123!",
    "confirmPassword": "Password123!"
}
 
### -----------------------------------------------
### 2. Login
### -----------------------------------------------
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/login
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "Password456!"
}
 
