### -----------------------------------------------
### 4. Logout
### -----------------------------------------------
# @name logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
 
### -----------------------------------------------
### 5. Verify Password
### -----------------------------------------------
# @name verifyPassword
POST {{baseUrl}}/verify-password
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
    "currentPassword": "Password123!"
}
 
